Package eu.monnetproject.data

Interfaces for generic access to data sources.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DataSource
    A source of data.
    DataTarget
    A target for data.
    RemoteRepository
    Interface for connecting to remote repositories.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FileDataSource
    A simple implementation that wraps a file as a data source
    FileDataTarget
    A simple implementation that wraps a file as a target
    PipeDataTarget
    A data target that pipes to a source.
    StringBufferTarget
    A data target that writes to a string buffer
    StringSource
    Implements a data source that reads from a given string
